    <lb n="6"/>ὁ καὶ <unclear>Πατευως</unclear> <unclear>υ</unclear>ἱ<supplied reason="lost">ὸς</supplied> τ<supplied reason="lost">οῦ μα</supplied>κ<unclear>α</unclear>ρίο<unclear>υ</unclear> Ἰσὰκ ὁ προγεγρα<unclear>μμ</unclear>ένος π<unclear>ε</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ποίημαι</supplied>

